  <brief_title>Tolerability of Enecadin (INN) in Acute Ischemic Stroke Trial - TEST</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicentre, Double-Blind, Randomised, Placebo-Controlled, Dose-Escalating Parallel-Group Study to Investigate the Tolerability of Enecadin (INN) in Acute Ischemic Stroke</official_title>
